articles.author: Adam Bankhurst
articles.title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom Disappoints In Its Debut But Still Wins the Domestic Weekend Box Office - IGN
articles.description: While Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom disappointed with debut earnings in North America reaching only $28.1 million, it was still enough for the last film in the DCEU to win the domestic weekend box office.
